                            <comment id="13989435" author="mreutegg" created="Mon, 5 May 2014 11:48:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added a test in revision &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1592487&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1592487&lt;/a&gt; (currently ignored).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a quick fix we can just disable garbage collection of previous documents. Documents for deleted nodes would still be collected.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13989468" author="mreutegg" created="Mon, 5 May 2014 12:44:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Implemented the quick fix described above in &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1592512&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1592512&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-1794&quot; title=&quot;Keep commit info for local changes in main document&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;OAK-1794&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;OAK-1794&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for a proper fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13989631" author="mreutegg" created="Mon, 5 May 2014 15:51:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merged into 1.0 branch in &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1592556&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1592556&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1592560&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1592560&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13990349" author="mreutegg" created="Tue, 6 May 2014 06:38:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Chetan pointed out that the empty type list will result in an incorrect query, which is not needed anyway with this quick fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13990357" author="mreutegg" created="Tue, 6 May 2014 06:53:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Done in &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1592665&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1592665&lt;/a&gt; (trunk) and &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1592667&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1592667&lt;/a&gt; (1.0).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
